The evidence with the title 'Reality check: has the U.S. borrowed more under Obama than all ... ' says Oct 19, 2016  ... While the large increase in borrowing occurred "under Obama," it's an overstatement to blame Obama's actions as the sole cause of the ballooning debt , according to the bipartisan Committee For A Responsible Federal Budget. The debt would have risen by $3 trillion because of tax and spending policies ... 
